name: Ashes °_°
description:
I am the skeleton in the closet /

the one you try to forget /

I am the remains of what was /

the memories you wish to forget /

I am the reminder of your past /

the one you try to ignore /

but I am always here /

haunting you in your dreams /

I am the bones and ashes /

of what once was /

and I will never go away.
